title: #92Noon! NFL Draft Rollout
description: All draft, all the time....with guests! Michael Lombardi analyzes in the opening segment, then we go back-to-back-back with NFC North opinions from Sinykin, Lions vox Dan Miller, Bears beat writer Dan Wiederer...Cy Amundson files his weekly social-distancing report, then more on the draft with Jordan Reid and Adam Caplan into the 11am hour!
